Params: {1: '600001', 2: 'The last test went well. Thank you, Liv.', 3: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/RoleCharacter/HasangNomal01.png', 4: '100000222', 7: '1'}
{1: '1000000', 2: "It's my duty. Everyone is counting on me.", 4: '100000229'}
{1: '600002', 2: "...It's our fault that we have to rely on you to do all this alone.", 3: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/RoleCharacter/XibokeladiNormal01.png', 4: '100000226', 7: '1'}
{1: '1000000', 2: "Someone has to do it. I'm glad that I have earned your trust.", 4: '100000230'}
{1: '1000000', 2: 'I know you picked the name Hippocrates to remind your students not to betray the oath they made.', 4: '100000231'}

{1: '1000000', 2: 'Just like the day I made my oath, I still wish to dedicate my life to the service of humanity. The well-being of my patients always comes first. I will respect the autonomy and dignity of all lives.', 4: '100000232'}
{1: '1000000', 2: "It is my greatest honor to be your student and grow under everyone's care.", 4: '100000233'}
{1: '1000000', 2: "That's why I will never forget the Hippocratic Oath. Because that is all I wish for.", 4: '100000234'}
{1: '600002', 2: "...It seems like there's nothing else I can teach you.", 3: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/RoleCharacter/XibokeladiNormal01.png', 4: '100000227', 7: '1'}

{1: '600001', 2: 'You will be landing in the abandoned church where Gray Raven and Chrome are. According to our locators, the twins are also approaching there.', 3: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/RoleCharacter/HasangNomal01.png', 4: '100000223', 7: '1'}

{1: '600001', 2: "We've successfully established communication. You can talk to them in the transport craft.", 3: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/RoleCharacter/HasangNomal01.png', 4: '100000224', 7: '1'}
{1: '600001', 2: "Liv... you're the hope of humanity. Save them.", 3: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/RoleCharacter/HasangNomal01.png', 4: '100000225', 7: '1'}
